Part two: Marina Bay MRT station The Circle line has a plethora of MRT (Mass Rapid Transit) station to choose from and I had chosen Marina Bay MRT station to write about. The Marina Bay MRT station has a unique station design and it is situated on a reclaimed land without any developed infrastructure surrounding it. It is also an underground MRT station that serves on the North South Line, Circle Line and the future Thomson Line. This essay comprises the description of the design and ornamentation
